{"tid":533492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國聯通布局5G建設　7大城市展開測試拚2年內商用","createTime":"2018-01-18T23:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T09:39:01.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"67dfbe6c8f435c499514cd9905ec294a58c44cb2","tid":533492,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3060/d3060031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3060%2Fd3060031.jpg&h=9feec73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲第一個國際5G標準預計將在2018年中訂出。（圖／路透社）<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n行動網路5G全球統一標準還沒有出來，但中國電信、中國聯通及中國移動等3大電信商已開始布局各城市。其中中國聯通的腳步很快，已計畫於北京、天津、上海、深圳、杭州、南京與雄安7個城市進行5G試驗，且不排除在未來增加更多試驗城市。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日經濟新聞》報導，中國聯通已向中國工信部提交申請，未來也會根據工信部、發改委的要求，增加試驗城市數量。中國聯通網路建設部副總經理馬紅兵日前透露，目前已經完成上海和深圳的外場建設，包括華為、中興和諾基亞的5G樣機試驗室驗證，以及部分外場性能驗證。<br />\n<br />\n除了中國聯通，中國電信處也在成都、雄安、深圳、上海、蘇州、蘭州等6座城市開通了5G測試點；中國移動方面則表示，已經建設了上海、廣州小規模外場，與懷柔外場形成互補。之後的規模試驗上，中國移動會在5大經濟發達（GDP排名全國前十）、交通便利、人口密度大的城市展開試點，網路規模達到500個基站，涉及26個場景，每個城市100個站。<br />\n<br />\n大陸工信部資訊通信發展司司長聞庫也提出四個建議，一是「遵從國際標準進程，加快推進預商用設備研發。」二是「發揮5G技術研發試驗平台，加快構建完整産業鏈。」三是「結合5G頻率規劃，同步推進3.5GHz和4.9GHz研發。」四是「促進業務應用發展，舉辦5G應用徵集大賽。」<br />\n<br />\n業界人士則指出，5G技術研發試驗第三階段規範已在16日頒布，預計在2018年底能達到商用水準，「試驗的城市會先比其他人早用到，2020年會實現5G正式商用。」<br />\n<br />\n▼5G將帶來更快的速度，以及更廣的覆蓋率。（圖／達志／示意圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1064/d1064969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1064%2Fd1064969.jpg&h=12f85467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180118/1095308.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180118%2F1095308.htm&d=s2b8xsje8RFwgfdUGlAbstr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=13b62200\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180118/1095308.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d9183cd28f62a55236380e03f4a3b4a8713c39ec","tid":533492,"uid":44454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:46:21.000Z","msg":"收唔到嘅，10G都冇用啦"},{"pid":"0cc436314c3767018bd94e2713429114c7c43c4f","tid":533492,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收唔到嘅，10G都冇用啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e39df0fd8edc4e1f77f5493fbf7c7622380d87","tid":533492,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5055a8502a639e105919cb0b1faeebd03a3e87eb","tid":533492,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:58:15.000Z","msg":"快又點，咪又係俾人監聽，咪又係要翻牆"},{"pid":"b87153c8b9097f4c0d0358ccffc709c85171fe72","tid":533492,"uid":84310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"All in 763<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997bb8943a8116f147684d3270d1f02d6ab834df","tid":533492,"uid":103230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"內聯網咁快做乜"},{"pid":"7cd1c0da35d6a5a56d7f47411af1cfc9c3c17cc2","tid":533492,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:07:29.000Z","msg":"竟然無廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dca2b97d61edb8c365cc44d4f18349cad9b8330","tid":533492,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d44a316527e036294ca5ad44b3ee32de0a12c274","tid":533492,"uid":44211,"like":